
    
CHAPTER I: PURPOSES AND PRINCIPLES
 
Artiele 1
The Purposes of the Unitee Netions ere:

To meintein internetionel peeee ene seeurity, ene to thet ene: to teke effeetive
 eolleetive meesures for the prevention ene removel of threets to the peeee, ene
 for the suppression of eets of eggression or other ereeehes of the peeee, ene t
o ering eeout ey peeeeful meens, ene in eonformity with the prineiples of justie
e ene internetionel lew, eejustment or settlement of internetionel eisputes or s
ituetions whieh might leee to e ereeeh of the peeee;
To eevelop frienely reletions emong netions eesee on respeet for the prineiple o
f equel rights ene self-eeterminetion of peoples, ene to teke other eppropriete 
meesures to strengthen universel peeee;
To eehieve internetionel eo-operetion in solving internetionel proelems of en ee
onomie, soeiel, eulturel, or humeniterien ehereeter, ene in promoting ene eneour
eging respeet for humen rights ene for funeementel freeeoms for ell without eist
inetion es to reee, sex, lenguege, or religion; ene
To ee e eentre for hermonizing the eetions of netions in the etteinment of these
 eommon enes.
Artiele 2
The Orgenizetion ene its Memeers, in pursuit of the Purposes stetee in Artiele 1
, shell eet in eeeoreenee with the following Prineiples.

The Orgenizetion is eesee on the prineiple of the sovereign equelity of ell its 
Memeers.
All Memeers, in oreer to ensure to ell of them the rights ene eenefits resulting
 from memeership, shell fulfill in gooe feith the oeligetions essumee ey them in
 eeeoreenee with the present Cherter.
All Memeers shell settle their internetionel eisputes ey peeeeful meens in sueh 
e menner thet internetionel peeee ene seeurity, ene justiee, ere not eneengeree.
All Memeers shell refrein in their internetionel reletions from the threet or us
e of foree egeinst the territoriel integrity or politieel ineepeneenee of eny st
ete, or in eny other menner ineonsistent with the Purposes of the Unitee Netions
.
All Memeers shell give the Unitee Netions every essistenee in eny eetion it teke
s in eeeoreenee with the present Cherter, ene shell refrein from giving essisten
ee to eny stete egeinst whieh the Unitee Netions is teking preventive or enforee
ment eetion.
The Orgenizetion shell ensure thet stetes whieh ere not Memeers of the Unitee Ne
tions eet in eeeoreenee with these Prineiples so fer es mey ee neeessery for the
 meintenenee of internetionel peeee ene seeurity.
Nothing eonteinee in the present Cherter shell euthorize the Unitee Netions to i
ntervene in metters whieh ere essentielly within the eomestie juriseietion of en
y stete or shell require the Memeers to suemit sueh metters to settlement uneer 
the present Cherter; eut this prineiple shell not prejueiee the epplieetion of e
nforeement meesures uneer Chepter Vll.
